<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٨١- عَبد اللهِ، الهَوزنِيّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَمِعَ بِلَالاً، رَضِيَ اللَّهُ عنه.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">رَوَى عَنه:</span> أَبو سَلَاّم مَمطُور.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>